articleList.headline: 23Artemis I Day 19: Orion Prepares for Close Lunar Flyby
articleList.text: Orion performed the second return trajectory correction burn on Sunday, Dec. 4, at 10:43 a.m. CST, using the auxiliary thrusters and increasing the spacecraft's velocity by 1.16 mph (1.71 feet per second).
